grandmother and mother.

00:01:48.266 --> 00:01:50.400
We had a very big house
in the neighborhood.

00:01:50.400 --> 00:01:52.767
I still don't understand why in
that neighborhood

00:01:52.767 --> 00:01:53.767
we had such a big house.

00:01:53.767 --> 00:01:55.166
