-- you know what I'm saying?
Get all that kinda good stuff,

00:11:51.300 --> 00:11:53.200
fill up an arena.

00:11:53.200 --> 00:11:55.367
For me to do that I gotta
come down like this.

00:11:55.367 --> 00:11:57.934
It's like a tricep work
so I got the Gatorade here --

00:11:57.934 --> 00:11:59.734
-- 'cause otherwise
I get cramps.

00:11:59.734 --> 00:12:01.600
My arm will do like that.

00:12:01.600 --> 00:12:05.333
So I had to, like,
I ended up sweating out

00:12:05.333 --> 00:12:07.433
my salt in my body.

00:12:07.433 --> 00:12:11.667
And so, uh, and then, of course,
you know,that's what we used to,

00:12:11.667 --> 00:12:16.300
you know, the gyrations
and physical grimaces

00:12:16.300 --> 00:12:18.934
and facial expressions and
stuff like that because

00:12:18.934 --> 00:12:21.300
between the emotions of the songs trying to do justice

00:12:21.300 --> 00:12:23.000
to the emotions of the lyrics

00:12:23.000 --> 00:12:26.700
as well as just the sheer pain between the fingers

